Do that many people even come?

569
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,400
Even if that many people show up,

570
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:49,040
how many are actually buying?

571
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:50,680
Each of us makes tens of thousands,

572
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:52,240
and it all ends up in the warehouse.

573
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:53,680
We're the ones who lose out.

574
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,440
Alright, since Erhu just spoke up,

575
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:58,760
let me reiterate.

576
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,320
Whether you do this or not,

577
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:02,080
everyone must think it through carefully.

578
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,720
You bear your own risk.

579
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:05,520
It's a willing agreement, alright?

580
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:08,240
Those who see this as an opportunity,

581
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,040
can come sign up with me now.

582
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:12,000
However much each of you wants to take,

583
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:13,160
however much you can make,

584
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,920
declare it yourselves, sign up yourselves.

585
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:17,120
But there's one thing I need to make clear.

586
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:20,800
Whatever you sign up for, you must deliver.

587
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:24,040
Because we're signing an agreement here.

588
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,000
Got it?

589
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,000
Got it, got it.

590
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,240
If you don't want in, that's fine too.

591
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,520
We won't force anyone.

592
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:29,880
But...

593
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:32,160
Today is your only chance to sign up.

594
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,080
Don't be like some people.

595
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:37,000
Getting jealous when others make money.

596
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:37,440
Right?

597
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,200
And then come running to me.

598
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,080
Sorry, but time waits for no one.

599
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:41,040
Now or never.

600
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:41,600
Alright?

601
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,440
Everyone clear on that?

602
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:42,680
Good.

603
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,240
You all got it?

604
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,800
Everyone had better think it through.

605
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:47,000
Chairman Xiao has already warned you all.

606
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,200
You bear your own risk.

607
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,560
You'd better think carefully.

608
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:51,240
Don't come crying to us later.

609
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:52,600
Brother Min.

610
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:54,000
I'm not targeting you here.

611
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,200
After all, this festival isn't yours to run.

612
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:59,200
Let me be the first to speak up.

613
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:00,560
This is our Peach Blossom Town's

614
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:03,600
first-ever Four Treasures Festival.

615
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:06,400
I'm a Peach Blossom Town local.

616
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:08,440
It wouldn't be right not to chip in.

617
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,440
Let me see.

618
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:11,720
I've filled in my numbers and signed it.

619
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:14,480
As a veteran business here,

620
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:16,040
I'd like to take part.

621
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:18,040
If it were anyone else, I wouldn't trust it.

622
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,680
But with Lin Yiran and Xuan Yan running it,

623
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,520
me,

624
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,240
I'm willing to bet on them.

625
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:23,920
Here's mine.

626
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:24,560
Don't bite off more than you can chew.

627
00:21:24,560 --> 00:21:25,440
I have to get in on this.

628
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,800
If you lose, no one's bailing you out.

629
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:27,240
Get out, get out.

630
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,560
I'll sign too, me too, me too!

631
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:31,840
Everyone gets one, don't push, here.

632
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,120
Everyone gets one, everyone.

633
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,720
Don't grab, don't grab!

634
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:36,080
Here.

635
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:37,280
Everyone gets one, everyone.

636
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,520
Hang it straight, sir.

637
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,880
Whatever you do, don't hang it crooked.

638
00:21:49,560 --> 00:21:53,240
It must show "Its torrent dashes down

639
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:54,160
three thousand feet from high, As if..."

640
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:56,000
Record it!

641
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:56,800
Record this too.

642
00:21:57,600 --> 00:21:58,400
Alright.

643
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:00,360
Don't hang it crooked, sir.

644
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:04,200
Make sure it shows "Its torrent dashes

645
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:06,000
down three thousand feet from high, As if..."

646
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,080
Zhang Bin!

647
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:10,120
What are you doing?

648
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:12,480
I told you to slow down.

649
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:14,680
Now you've ruined it.

650
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:15,960
So sorry, Director Liao.

651
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:18,480
You must be very, very careful.

652
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:18,840
Yes, yes.

653
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:19,480
Alright, alright, Director Liao.

654
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,880
I'll be careful, I'll be careful.

655
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,880
Just ahead is our hotel's little bar.

656
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:05,680
You can grab a drink and chat here.

657
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:58,920
Sister Yi.

658
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:01,040
Yiran, you're here.

659
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:01,800
All right.

660
00:24:02,120 --> 00:24:03,360
Money Goddess, hand over the cash.

661
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:04,160
What money?

662
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:06,520
These two payments.

663
00:24:06,520 --> 00:24:08,440
The deposit for the AR system equipment.

664
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,880
We need to wire it to them.

665
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,480
And there's more.

666
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:12,400
Construction fee for the China Chic Zone.

667
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:15,040
Plus I've got 20,000 in cash to cover.

668
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,640
My pockets are completely empty.

669
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:17,840
Where's the approval form?

670
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:19,360
The form?

671
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:20,400
Wait.

672
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,600
Didn't Deputy Mayor Luo sign it for you?

673
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,600
He didn't give it to me.

674
00:24:24,040 --> 00:24:24,880
Did he give it to you?

675
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:25,640
No.

676
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:26,880
Little Zheng.

677
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,080
Do you know anything?

678
00:24:28,080 --> 00:24:28,840
No idea.

679
00:24:29,120 --> 00:24:30,560
I saw Deputy Mayor Luo this morning.

680
00:24:30,560 --> 00:24:32,080
He didn't mention it either.

681
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,560
Um, Sister Yi.

682
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:35,360
This is really an emergency right now.

683
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:38,040
Could you maybe go find Director Huang?

684
00:24:38,040 --> 00:24:39,200
Make a special exception for this?

685
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:41,080
No way, that's against procedure.

686
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:44,800
Fine.

687
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:45,800
Thanks anyway, Sister Yi.

688
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:47,920
Deputy Mayor Luo, I give up on him.

689
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:50,200
We've only got one week left.

690
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:52,080
If the China Chic Zone funds don't arrive,

691
00:24:52,080 --> 00:24:54,200
it'll be too late for real.

692
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:56,640
More anxious than the person involved.

693
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,320
The China Chic Zone funds

694
00:24:58,320 --> 00:25:00,600
were already in the overall budget, no?

695
00:25:00,600 --> 00:25:01,600
Who could've known?

696
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:06,680
The powerful are shortsighted and cannot plan ahead.

697
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,720
What does that mean?

698
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:13,400
It's from middle school classical Chinese.

699
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,720
How did you pass Chinese class?

700
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:18,640
Sorry, Teacher Liao, my bad.

701
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:20,080
Taozi.

702
00:25:20,080 --> 00:25:20,880
Sister Yiran.

703
00:25:21,760 --> 00:25:23,080
How'd it go? Got the money?

704
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:24,080
No.

705
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:26,400
Do you know where Deputy Mayor Luo is?

706
00:25:26,840 --> 00:25:28,120
When he stopped by yesterday,

707
00:25:28,120 --> 00:25:29,080
I overheard him say

708
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,480
he was going to the county today

709
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,360
for the county economic conference.

710
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,760
The Literati Gathering is half done.

711
00:25:35,840 --> 00:25:37,320
The other projects haven't even started.

712
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:39,320
For our Four Treasures Culture Festival,

713
00:25:39,320 --> 00:25:40,080
the biggest highlight

714
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:42,120
and main work are in the China Chic Zone.

715
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,640
If we can't pull it off,

716
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:45,120
it'll be exactly what people say,

717
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,080
a vanity project.

718
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:47,600
Don't stress.

719
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:50,680
As long as we do our best, that's enough.

720
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,280
Right, don't worry.

721
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,320
We've all done our best.

722
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:54,240
Even if they pin the blame,

723
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,720
it's got nothing to do with you.

724
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,640
But the key work isn't done well.

725
00:25:58,080 --> 00:25:58,880
That's true.

726
00:25:58,880 --> 00:25:59,640
Sister Yiran.

727
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:00,720
Sister Yiran.

728
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:03,440
Deputy Mayor Luo is back from the county.

729
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:05,040
Where is he?

730
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:06,600
At President Xiao Min's factory.

731
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,800
You keep working, I'll go find him.

732
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:09,840
Slow down.

733
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:11,000
Slow down, Sister Yiran!

734
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,240
China's traditional festivals

735
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,080
carry deep cultural meaning

736
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:16,720
and rich folk traditions.

737
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:19,160
So the festive atmosphere

738
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,280
is really important.

739
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:22,320
That gives the couplet market

740
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,920
tons of business opportunities.

741
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,040
And what really sustains

742
00:26:26,040 --> 00:26:28,200
a factory of our size

743
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,960
is products like Everlasting Red,

744
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:32,280
things that can reach every household.

745
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:32,920
That's great.

746
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,680
Aren't you busy with the festival?

747
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:40,920
Why are you here at my place?

748
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,320
I'm not looking for you.

749
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:43,600
I'm looking for Deputy Mayor Luo.

750
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:48,560
He's right up ahead.

751
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:49,640
Deputy Mayor Luo.

752
00:26:49,760 --> 00:26:50,560
Deputy Mayor Luo.

753
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,560
What are you up to now?

754
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,360
The funding approval.

755
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,840
Didn't you say you'd signed it?

756
00:26:58,840 --> 00:27:01,040
Can't you see I'm with the leadership?

757
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:02,840
No, Deputy Mayor Luo.

758
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,640
I had no choice.

759
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:05,080
I had to come find you here.

760
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,240
I'll keep it short.

761
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,480
The Ink Wash Theater,

762
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:09,080
and the Metaverse Treasure Hunt,

763
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,480
are all waiting to move in and set up.

764
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,840
Literati Gathering's second payment isn't paid.

765
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,280
The workers have all stopped.

766
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:15,720
Everyone's waiting to restart.

767
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:18,840
Haven't I already told you?

768
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:21,480
The funds from above don't arrive that fast.

769
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:23,800
The town is scraping it together

770
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,080
bit by bit for you.

771
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,320
Does anxiety put food on the table?

772
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:28,120
Anything else?

773
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,360
There's less than a week left.

774
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,080
How can I not be anxious?

775
00:27:30,080 --> 00:27:31,000
Watch your attitude.

776
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,240
The finance office,

777
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:35,720
the finance office said

778
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,680
there's still over 100,000 in special funds.

779
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:39,480
That's enough to support this project.

780
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:40,360
So why are you

781
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,840
saying there isn't any?

782
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,600
Anyway, you're the person in charge.

783
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:46,080
If anything goes wrong,

784
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:47,600
you'll have to take responsibility.

785
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:51,680
Put the China Chic Zone on hold for now.

786
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,880
Wait for further notice.

787
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,000
Why?

788
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:56,520
Someone will tell you why.

789
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:58,600
No, Deputy Mayor Luo.

790
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,640
This is ridiculous.

791
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,520
Hello?

792
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,800
Director Lin.

793
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,280
Come to the town office right away.

794
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,480
Yes, right now.

795
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,680
I have something to tell you.

796
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:20,120
Director Ge.

797
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,160
Director Lin, you're finally here.

798
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,560
The party committee is about to meet.

799
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,680
Secretary Peng asked you to attend.

800
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:30,000
Deputy Mayor Luo is here too.

801
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:31,680
I'm here, waiting just for you.

802
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,960
Just to give you a heads-up in advance.

803
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:36,640
Don't get angry, control your emotions.

804
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,800
Why was the China Chic Zone shut down?

805
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:44,440
By the rules,

806
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:46,280
I really shouldn't tell you.

807
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,440
But, you know,

808
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,720
I'm worried about your temper.

809
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:52,320
A senior official called Secretary Peng,

810
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,080
saying our Four Treasures Festival

811
00:28:54,080 --> 00:28:55,320
is being rushed a bit.

812
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:57,080
Especially the China Chic Zone design.

813
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,360
It wasn't thoroughly vetted.

814
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,800
It might cause unexpected consequences.

815
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:02,800
So they suggested our party committee

816
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:04,040
be more rigorous and cautious.

817
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,280
Think it through fully first.

818
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,880
Less than a week left, think about what?

819
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:09,960
The more urgent, the more cautious.

820
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:12,240
This Four Treasures Festival will be great.

821
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:14,160
It'll blow people away.

822
00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:16,600
I know, I understand.

823
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:18,560
Secretary Peng kept praising you nonstop.

824
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:19,600
She hasn't stopped.

825
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,040
It's not time to give up yet.

826
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:21,920
Cheer up.

827
00:29:26,080 --> 00:29:26,800
Let's go.

828
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:35,440
Don't give Secretary Peng a hard time.

829
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:37,320
She's under a lot of pressure too.

830
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:42,360
Got it.

831
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:45,840
Secretary.

832
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,040
Come in.

833
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,760
Come, have a seat.

834
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:50,560
Sit here.

835
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,360
I'll just sit in the back.

836
00:29:53,360 --> 00:29:53,760
Sit.

837
00:29:57,560 --> 00:29:58,280
Lin Yiran.

838
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:02,400
We invited you to today's committee meeting

839
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:04,920
because we have some questions

840
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:06,600
we'd like to ask you.

841
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:07,400
Little Lin,

842
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:09,680
the promotional work you've done lately

843
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,600
is really spot on.

844
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:12,280
Great work.

845
00:30:13,520 --> 00:30:16,600
I'd like to know about safety concerns

846
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:19,920
and what the daily foot traffic will be.

847
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:22,000
Our current registration system

848
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,760
shows over 4,000 people signed up.

849
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,480
In the final week,

850
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:27,040
daily traffic will increase significantly.

851
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:29,080
I estimate during the three-day event,

852
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:31,080
daily traffic won't be under 3,000 people.

853
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:33,520
That's quite a lot.

854
00:30:34,360 --> 00:30:36,800
So for security work,

855
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,680
