857
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:46,360
Deputy Mayor Luo has been handling it.

858
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,240
Right.

859
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:50,000
I've been handling it,

860
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:52,200
but Director Lin,

861
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:55,800
the attendance numbers you gave me

862
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,120
keep changing.

863
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,960
They increase every day.

864
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:01,200
Even now, you haven't given me

865
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,240
