870
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:14,760
I must follow your guidance and orders.

871
00:31:18,520 --> 00:31:19,160
Alright.

872
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:22,200
If security falls directly under me,

873
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:25,800
I'd set up a three-tier command center

874
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:28,240
with a chief and a deputy commander.

875
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:30,400
Then in each functional zone,

876
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:32,320
I'd assign a person in charge,

877
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:35,120
each managing grid teams, patrol teams,

878
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:36,880
and emergency response mobile units.

879
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,800
Then in each functional zone,

880
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:39,920
we'd station a volunteer

881
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,280
to help maintain visitor order.

882
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:46,200
County security, fire, and medical

883
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,200
will be on the perimeter.

884
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:50,120
The deputy commander will coordinate these,

885
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:52,680
working with each zone's supervisor

886
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:54,920
to implement crowd control measures.

887
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:56,880
Finally, I'd set up

888
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,200
a four-tier emergency response system

889
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,200
with contingency plans in place.

890
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:01,960
Especially, all security personnel must be

891
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:03,160
organized and trained.

892
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:05,040
For stampede prevention

893
00:32:05,120 --> 00:32:06,560
and other emergencies,

894
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:09,720
ensure everyone can evacuate and respond.

895
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:13,000
Then at the main entrances

896
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:14,280
and indoor areas,

897
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,280
set up two-person security checkpoints

898
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:18,400
with dedicated staff to assist.

899
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:20,760
Set up fire, explosion, and medical stations.

900
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:26,600
I'm sorry, everyone.

901
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:28,120
Because I didn't prepare beforehand,

902
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:29,520
that's all I can share for now.

903
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:30,280
Of course,

904
00:32:30,280 --> 00:32:31,440
if you all need it,

905
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:32,440
I can put together

906
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:34,720
a detailed security implementation plan.

907
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,280
How about it?

908
00:32:38,600 --> 00:32:41,480
Does anyone have any other thoughts?

909
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:47,000
If no one has anything to add,

910
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:49,200
I'd like to share my thoughts.

911
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:49,920
Go ahead.

912
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:55,440
Director Lin is sharp-minded and logical,

913
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,200
and a fast learner too.

914
00:32:57,920 --> 00:33:00,720
But I still feel

915
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:03,520
she lacks experience handling

916
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,120
a China Chic expo of this scale.

917
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,440
I also believe

918
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:09,200
she has seriously

919
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:11,440
studied the relevant knowledge.

920
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:13,960
So if you ask

921
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:16,360
whether her points make sense,

922
00:33:16,360 --> 00:33:17,120
yes, they do.

923
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,240
But these aren't her own insights.

924
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:21,800
They're from books, from other people.

925
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:25,400
If any unexpected incident occurs,

926
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,440
I believe

927
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:29,800
with only her theoretical knowledge,

928
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:32,280
she may not be able to perfectly handle

929
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,920
such an emergency.

930
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:35,440
That's precisely why

931
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:38,280
we need collective decision-making,

932
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:41,160
and we need to pool everyone's ideas.

933
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:42,480
So on the matter

934
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,560
of setting up a China Chic Zone

935
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:47,680
at the Four Treasures Culture Festival,

936
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:49,160
my view is

937
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:51,640
we should be cautious.

938
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,760
Everyone,

939
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,360
any other questions?

940
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,160
Feel free to speak up.

941
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,280
Let me say a few words first.

942
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,400
Before this meeting,

943
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:21,920
I searched online for some info,

944
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:24,760
and found a few typical cases.

945
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:25,960
I'd like to share them

946
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:27,400
with all of you here.

947
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:31,920
In one place down south,

948
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:33,280
they held an expo.

949
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:38,400
Two underage girls, fifteen or sixteen,

950
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:42,080
wore tight miniskirts and fishnets,

951
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:44,960
dancing up on that stage.

952
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:48,120
The online backlash was massive.

953
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:51,080
You can imagine the impact.

954
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,679
It was extremely harmful.

955
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,480
In another place,

956
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:56,040
because it got insanely popular,

957
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,240
the scalpers

958
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:00,120
seized the opportunity.

959
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:03,160
They organized a crowd of tourists

960
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:04,560
to storm

961
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:05,880
the ticket gates.

962
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,360
It nearly

963
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:09,960
caused a stampede.

964
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,680
If we make

965
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:14,240
young people chasing trends

966
00:35:14,680 --> 00:35:16,040
the main tone of the event,

967
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:16,960
then,

968
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:17,920
from the perspective

969
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:20,480
of Four Treasures industry insiders,

970
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:23,000
how would they feel about it?

971
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,840
Everyone, remember this:

972
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,160
our Peach Blossom Town

973
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:28,880
is built on the Xuan paper industry.

974
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:31,120
If the Four Treasures Culture Festival

975
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,400
turns into a youth entertainment show,

976
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,960
then the real

977
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:37,960
Four Treasures consumers,

978
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:38,960
sellers,

979
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,320
and peers in brush, ink, and inkstone,

980
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,480
how would they view it?

981
00:35:42,720 --> 00:35:45,560
Could it still be called that festival?

982
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,840
Would anyone still come in the future?

983
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:48,720
Am I right?

984
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:34,360
During the meeting,

985
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,120
don't give Secretary Peng a hard time.

986
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:38,080
She's under a lot of pressure too.

987
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:41,600
This is all just armchair strategizing.

988
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:44,280
My advice is to proceed with caution.

989
00:37:06,120 --> 00:37:08,160
Nobody's in the mood anymore.

990
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,360
What's with all of you?

991
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,600
Completely dejected.

992
00:37:14,600 --> 00:37:15,920
Everyone's so listless.

993
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:18,440
Is it because Lin Yiran's not here?

994
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:20,440
There was a notice in the group.

995
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:22,520
The China Chic event is suspended.

996
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,960
Suspended?

997
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:25,080
Yeah.

998
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:27,120
There are only six days left.

999
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:28,160
Suspending it now,

1000
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:30,280
that's basically a death sentence.

1001
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:33,080
I don't get what the higher-ups think.

1002
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,520
It was such a great project.

1003
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:42,800
Off work. Going home.

1004
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:45,520
Wait a bit longer.

1005
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:47,280
Let's wait for Sister Yiran to arrive.

1006
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:48,880
What's the point of waiting?

1007
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,600
The China Chic Zone is suspended.

1008
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:52,440
Why stay here?

1009
00:37:52,680 --> 00:37:53,360
Let's go.

1010
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:55,080
Going home.

1011
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,400
Sister Yiran is here.

1012
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,560
You're back.

1013
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:27,800
Stop dwelling on it.

1014
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,320
Sit, sit, sit.

1015
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,520
Come on, listen.

1016
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:44,960
I have a suggestion.

1017
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:47,080
We should celebrate properly.

1018
00:38:48,040 --> 00:38:48,840
Celebrate?

1019
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:51,800
Xuan Yan, did the scolding fry your brain?

1020
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,560
Taozi, have you been spending

1021
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:54,760
all your time with Lin Yiran

1022
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,280
until the hustle made you dumb?

1023
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:57,160
Working ourselves to death,

1024
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,160
not earning a single cent.

1025
00:38:58,480 --> 00:39:00,320
Now that we've finally broken free,

1026
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:02,200
we've gotta celebrate properly!

1027
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,360
Exactly.

1028
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,200
Right?

1029
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,720
Sister Yiran's hustle really made me

1030
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:11,120
lose myself for a while.

1031
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,200
This is so much better now.

1032
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,960
No more work, no more stress.

1033
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,720
Happiness came a bit too suddenly.

1034
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,960
Reminds me of my motto:

1035
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:20,240
If you can't hustle, just lie flat.

1036
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:21,360
If you can't lie flat, just roll.

1037
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:22,360
If you can't roll, just sleep.

1038
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:24,400
Thank you, Xuan Yan.

1039
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:25,720
You helped me find myself again.

1040
00:39:27,560 --> 00:39:28,400
Look at you.

1041
00:39:28,560 --> 00:39:30,160
Waiting for dusk at dawn,

1042
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:33,360
waiting for dawn at dusk.

1043
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:34,960
Three meals to fill the belly,

1044
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:37,520
four seasons lying flat on the bed.

1045
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:39,720
Thank you, teacher.

1046
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:41,640
Thank you for the lovely blessing.

1047
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,320
You don't even get it, "lovely blessing"?

1048
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:47,920
Director Liao, they don't teach this.

1049
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:48,800
What do you mean?

1050
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:50,560
You need a class to understand this?

1051
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,480
It's plain as day.

1052
00:39:52,480 --> 00:39:54,560
coasting through life.

1053
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:57,040
Director, that's too much!

1054
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,680
I've noticed that ever since

1055
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:00,720
you became the tourism spokesperson,

1056
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:02,400
you've really let it go to your head.

1057
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,720
Sister Yiran, let me tell you,

1058
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,840
ever since Director Liao faced reality,

1059
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,360
he's really been letting loose.

1060
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:12,280
I told him short videos need no scripts,

1061
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,360
but he insisted on writing them.

1062
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,680
And the stuff he writes...

1063
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,360
it really gets in your head.

1064
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:18,640
Cheer up.

1065
00:40:18,640 --> 00:40:19,960
Let me read you a passage.

1066
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:26,760
Rigorous, careful, error-free.

1067
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,800
Taozi, pick a passage

1068
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:31,760
and read it out loud.

1069
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:33,320
You got it.

1070
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,280
Let me find one.

1071
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,280
Let's go with this part.

1072
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:42,080
The Xuan ancestor, Xuan Zhengdao,

1073
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:46,160
mixed sandalwood bark and sandy rice straw

1074
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:49,200
adding Huangshan Hot Spring Jade Powder.

1075
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:50,880
After one hundred days,

1076
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:53,480
blood streaks appeared in the pulp.

1077
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:56,080
The Sandalwood King sensed the slaughter

1078
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:58,400
and resisted with tree spirit's blood.

1079
00:40:58,880 --> 00:41:01,200
Then the An Lushan Rebellion broke out.

1080
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,040
Rebel forces chased their prey here.

1081
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:07,200
Xuan Zhengdao poured the pulp into the fire.

1082
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,000
A miracle appeared.

1083
00:41:10,120 --> 00:41:13,320
A white paper curtain rose from the blaze,

1084
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,520
and every single arrow

1085
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,560
was blocked and sent back.

1086
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:21,200
The Xuan ancestor became a war god!

1087
00:41:23,640 --> 00:41:24,560
What's so funny?

1088
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,920
Tell me, isn't that captivating?

1089
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:31,880
I've studied the short video playbook.

1090
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:33,440
It boils down to four words:

1091
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:35,320
Traffic is king.

1092
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,000
Traffic is king, huh?

1093
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:37,800
Director,

1094
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:40,400
you've really figured out the internet.

1095
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:42,440
But we're using Xuan paper history

1096
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,560
to promote the Four Treasures Festival.

1097
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,160
You're turning it into Strange Tales.

1098
00:41:46,160 --> 00:41:47,240
Is that even reliable?

1099
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:48,680
How is it not reliable?

1100
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:52,120
The main historical figures and events

1101
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:54,480
line up with the timeline.

1102
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:57,560
Sure, with a bit of artistic license,

1103
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,920
but who says it's not allowed?

1104
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:02,320
Still, you can't just make stuff up.

1105
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,560
Right, Sister Yiran?

1106
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:13,160
Enough, let's go.

1107
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:16,040
Worked to the bone and didn't earn a cent.

1108
00:42:16,160 --> 00:42:18,280
Don't you owe me a farewell dinner?

1109
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,840
Come on, my treat.

1110
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:21,800
Dinner's fine, same old rule.

1111
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:22,840
AA.

1112
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,000
I'm exhausted to death.

1113
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,520
Can't someone treat me for once?

1114
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:26,360
Lin Yiran,

1115
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:27,720
everyone's tired.

1116
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:29,080
But the rule can't change.

1117
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,160
It's a principle.

1118
00:42:30,160 --> 00:42:31,640
We must go AA.

1119
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:34,240
Come on, let's go eat.

1120
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:35,840
Let's go, go, go.

1121
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:37,000
Come on, let's eat.

1122
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:37,840
Let's go!

1123
00:42:39,120 --> 00:42:40,360
Food, food, food!

1124
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,000
Let's go, go, go.

1125
00:42:46,160 --> 00:42:46,840
You settle the bill later.

1126
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:48,480
Fifty per person, no more.

1127
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,400
Director, you...

1128
00:42:50,480 --> 00:42:51,560
Anything over, I'll cover.

1129
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:53,520
What do you mean, you'll cover?

